function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	--Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idRunestone, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idRunestone, false)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idDummyGizmo)
	
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idRunestone, S_CHARGED_EFFECT)


	-- Activate remaining wraiths if gizmo is operated before they are active
	for i, idWraith in pairs (tMonsters) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idWraith) then
			Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idWraith, false)
			Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idWraith, true)
		end
	end

	Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idActorPlayer, "QST_Scos_TheDiviner_Runestone02_Active")

end

function Start(listValidActors, idActorDetector)

	-- Checks to see if a player is within the trigger volume and has the Hazel-Witch Ley Buff so
	-- it unhides the runestone and makes it interactable.
	-- Its giving a count for the number of valid players here too

	nPlayer = 0
	
	for u, idActor in pairs(listValidActors) do

		if Hydra.ActorIsPlayer(idActor) then
			
			nPlayer = nPlayer + 1
			
			bHasBuff = Hydra.BuffIsOnActor(sPower, idBuff, idActor)
			
			if bHasBuff then
				Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idRunestone, false)
				Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idRunestone, false)
				
				-- One time spawn monsters. Set them to disabled to activate later
				if bSpawnMonsters then
				
					Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(idSpawnerWoodWraith)
					tMonsters = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Scos_TheDiviner_MonsterGrp")
										
					for u, idMonster in pairs(tMonsters) do
						Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idMonster, true)
						Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idMonster, false)
					end
					
					bSpawnMonsters = false
					UF_SpawnWaves()
				end
						 
				bBuffedPlayerInTrigger = true
				break
			else
				bBuffedPlayerInTrigger = false
			end
		end
	end

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idRunestone, true)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idRunestone, true)
	
	bBuffedPlayerInTrigger = false

function UF_SpawnWaves()

	nCounter = nCounter + 1

	tMonsters = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Scos_TheDiviner_MonsterGrp")
	idMonster = tMonsters[1]
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idMonster) then
		if nCounter == 1 then
			Hydra.Wait(2)
			Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idMonster, false)
			Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idMonster, true)
		end

	end
